{"tid":2427181,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"著黑衫VS抵制黑衫","createTime":"2021-02-28T15:10:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-01T00:18:57.000Z","uid":211994,"like":18,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"41e7a1436da5e592eb91ee4571df929ea31d9689","tid":2427181,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T15:10:20.000Z","msg":"見到依家分咗兩邊（主要都係IG啲文宣）<br />\n<br />\n「成本低，少少事都唔做？」VS「冇用，形式主義」<br />\n<br />\n可能俾人當分化撚<br />\n但如果大家真係可以坐低討論下就最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n樓主自己諗法：定好自己行事準則，之後再決定要點樣行動"},{"pid":"1f9ef9b01b5da61013d3d18dbf9fffe9bca8fff6","tid":2427181,"uid":252541,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T15:11:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YWjGzTh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYWjGzTh.jpg&h=58d7870c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1b537c36bf5a630d05e2df3dadfd85f5a752a07f","tid":2427181,"uid":65790,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T15:16:05.000Z","msg":"著黑衫都要諗？<br />\n想著咪著"},{"pid":"cb74cb31888f8c7893966baa339bbe80f8e637f6","tid":2427181,"uid":288370,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T15:20:13.000Z","msg":"如果連少少事都唔做嘅話，到需要做大事嗰陣，更加唔會有人出嚟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有個無成本無風險嘅行動，希望大家響應 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【請推行動 po】真係好嬲好嬲，然後聽日繼續返工？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2426872\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2426872</a>"},{"pid":"d32a24d03e088953c38ab1db86c6c1cbb4f3e2bc","tid":2427181,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T15:20:54.000Z","msg":"，"},{"pid":"b5ec6f504f4f9ba562aa2abca0ac19028534ee1a","tid":2427181,"uid":189754,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"1b537c36bf5a630d05e2df3dadfd85f5a752a07f","tid":2427181,"uid":65790,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy"